{"word":"χύσις","slug":"χύσις","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>χύσις</b></el> <el>(χύ˘σις, εως,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:χέω'><el>χέω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>a flood, stream</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>of dry things, <i>a heap</i>, <el>φύλλων χ.</el> <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>: <i>a quantity</i>, <el>σαρκῶν</el> <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b><a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a> of <i>the lapse</i> of time, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}